sparql_query_info.imp:
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
        PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
        PREFIX ep: <http://linkedu.eu/dedalo/explanationPattern.owl#>
        PREFIX eo: <https://purl.org/heals/eo#>
        PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>
        PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/>
        PREFIX food: <http://purl.org/heals/food/>
        PREFIX prov: <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#>
        PREFIX provone: <http://purl.org/provone#>
        PREFIX sio:<http://semanticscience.org/resource/>
        SELECT distinct ?value where {
  <{obj}> prov:qualifiedGeneration ?a1  .
  ?a1 provone:hadEntity  ?value  .
}
param_desc: The URI of the starting object.
return_desc: The resulting values from the path traversal.
